	(text "Note: The values generated\nby this lookup table do not\nappear to make any sense.\n\nEx. C15 (MSB) ought to put\nout all 0s, then switch to\nall 1s at some point.\n(i.e. 00000000011111111)\n\nC17 should probably have\n2 groups like that\n(i.e. 00000011100111111)\n\nNot seeing those patterns."
